       â”œâ”€â”€ ProfileForm
       â””â”€â”€ PasswordForm
```

---

# ğŸ§  When NOT to Split

Donâ€™t split if:

âŒ Component is very small
âŒ Used only once and very simple
âŒ Splitting makes it more complicated

Over-splitting is also bad.

---

# ğŸ”¥ Golden Rule (Very Important)

If you cannot explain what the component does in one sentence â†’
It is probably doing too much.

---

# ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» For You Venky (Developer Thinking)

