Component splitting = Breaking large class into smaller classes.

Cleaner architecture. Easier debugging.

---

# ğŸ¯ Interview Answer (Short Version)

You should split components when:

* The component becomes too large
* Parts of UI can be reused
* A section has its own state or logic
* To improve readability and maintainability

